    class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-[-0.02em] text-black dark:text-white md:text-7xl md:leading-[5rem]"
  >
    Contact Us
  </h1>

  <p class="my-16 text-xl">
    If you wish to book a session, a masterclass, request a quote or simply have
    a chat with us, please send us an e-mail at
  </p>

  <FlipText
    className="text-2xl tracking-[-0.1em] text-black dark:text-white md:text-6xl md:leading-[5rem]"
